    "description": "Try your hand at plant-based protein with this sticky, sweet tofu bowl. You'll top rice with creamy slaw, peanut-smothered cucumber and crispy tofu. Drizzle with a sticky red chilli relish and dig in. Source of protein. Protein contributes to a growth in muscle mass.",
